## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="30af6-130">下列 C# 範例示範如何列舉所指定的通用類別目錄伺服器<xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext>物件，並列印至標準主控台每個通用類別目錄伺服器儲存每一個屬性的一般名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30af6-130">The following C# example shows how to enumerate the global catalog servers in the specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext> object and print the common name of each property stored on each global catalog server to the standard console.</span></span>  

```csharp  

foreach (GlobalCatalog gc in GlobalCatalog.FindAll(context))  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(gc.Name);  

    foreach (ActiveDirectorySchemaProperty prop in gc.FindAllProperties())  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine(prop.CommonName);  
    }  
}  

```
